msgid "help_main_slide1_title"
msgstr "Daily Practice"

msgid "help_main_slide1_text"
msgstr "Practice is open to everyone.\n\nEvery day brings a new mandala based on today's date.\n\nUse it for a short daily ritual and keep your practice journal."

msgid "help_main_slide2_title"
msgstr "Personal Collection"

msgid "help_main_slide2_text"
msgstr "Collection shows your personal mandalas as on-chain NFTs.\n\nA birth date or another meaningful date can exist in one copy only.\n\nEach mandala belongs to one owner."

msgid "help_main_slide3_title"
msgstr "Claim Yours"

msgid "help_main_slide3_text"
msgstr "Mint your personal mandala on the website.\n\nConnect your wallet, link it with your watch, and unlock your collection."

msgid "help_main_slide3_action"
msgstr "Scan to mint & link"

